## üèÜ Why JX Logger?

| Feature | Standard Logging | JX Logger |
|---------|------------------|-----------|
| **Rich Output** | ‚ùå Plain text | ‚úÖ Colors, emojis, formatting |
| **Async Support** | ‚ùå Blocking | ‚úÖ Non-blocking queue-based |
| **Data Masking** | ‚ùå Manual | ‚úÖ Automatic |
| **Performance Monitoring** | ‚ùå None | ‚úÖ Built-in metrics |
| **Contextual Info** | ‚ùå Limited | ‚úÖ Rich context tracking |
| **Custom Levels** | ‚ùå Basic | ‚úÖ SUCCESS, TRACE + icons |
| **JSON Structured** | ‚ùå Manual setup | ‚úÖ Built-in |
| **Easy Setup** | ‚ö†Ô∏è Complex | ‚úÖ One-liner |

